Attribute.value: Treasury has identified a sophisticated cyber-enabled  ATM cash out campaign we are calling  FASTCash.  FASTCash  has been active since late 2016 targeting banks in Africa and Asia to  remotely  compromise payment  switch  application servers within banks to facilitate fraudulent transactions, primarily involving ATMs to steal cash equivalent to tens of millions of dollars
